profile_process_audio::text_card_0::text: Sagalee adeemsicha ibsuuf barbaachisurratti xiyyeeffadhu. Kan si barbaachisu waan hunda miti, tarkaanfiiwwan adeemsicha jalqabarraa hanga xumuraatti agarsiisan ga'oodha.
profile_process_audio::title: Adeemsa odeeffannoo Dhuunfaa
profile_process_audio::clip_card_3::goal: Adeemsicha keessatti tarkaanfii taatichaa barbaachisaa itti aanu waraabi.
profile_process_audio::clip_card_0::goal: Yeroo isaan adeemsicha jalqabuuf qophaa'an waraabi. Akkamitti qophaa'u?
profile_process_audio::text_card_1::text: Sagalee bifa garagaraatiin waraabi - yeroo qaamichi ibsu, sagalee adeemsicha keessatti jijjiirama yookaan tarkaanfii adda ta'e agarsiisu.
profile_process_audio::clip_card_4::goal: Sagalee hordoftootatti waan ta'aa jiru himu waraabi.
profile_process_audio::clip_card_6::goal: Yeroo qaamichi adeemsicha xumuru waraabi. Sirriitti kan mul'isu, bareedaadha.
profile_process_audio::clip_card_1::goal: Jalqaba adeemsichaa yookaan tarkaanfii jalqabaa adeemsichaa waraabi.
profile_process_audio::clip_card_5::goal: Yoo seenaankee waa'ee waan taatichi hordoftoof yookaan namoota ilaalanii godhu ta'e, deebii gochaa isaanii waraabi.
profile_process_audio::clip_card_7::goal: Seenicha xumuri, akka inni itti xumure nutti himi.
profile_process_audio::clip_card_2::goal: Sagalee bakka adeemsichi itti ta'aa jiruu waraabi.
